This is my first Tower Defense's map,

- It has got 27 levels of 10 Pokemons. 
- It has got 3 BOSS (Lugia (11000 HP), Mewtwo (17500 HP) and Togepi (20000 HP)).
- You've got 20 lifes.  
- When you kill a BOSS, you win all your lifes.

* Mani Admin Plugin is nesecarry to have money all the 10 seconds.
* Auto-Sniper and Machine Gun are the bests weapons.
